attributionInfo.brokerName: The Dream Realty By Valeria Navas LLC

data.description: PRICE REDUCED BY $15K.  Fantastic Opportunity to own a home on 4.46 acres in the country, but close to amenities of a city. This home features little to no steps into main level, 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, kitchen, living room, dining area, and single attached garage, and double detached carport. Large covered front porch, large covered back deck off of dining area. Lower level features lots of room for storage, bathroom with shower and toilet, sink is outside of bathroom, garage door and interior access through the upstairs garage.  Wood stove with blower system in basement for those cold nights or just to save energy. Covered parking in back for RV and a couple of cars.  Detached garage and several out buildings remain.  Somewhat level yard, owner had a garden.  Home needs work, mostly cosmetic. Some soft spots in the bathroom.  Home is an estate and is being cleaned out.
